Title: ChosunUniv RoseFestival
TodayRoseDesc: Let me tell you about today's blooming situation
NotesForVisitorsDesc: We will inform you of precautions when viewing
Guide1: The rose garden is open from 9:00 to 21:00
Guide2: Do not stand or sit on the curb
Guide3: Go into the rose field You can't touch the roses
Guide4: Bicycles, kickboards, etc. Can't bring it in
Guide5: You cannot bring pets to the rose garden
Guide6: Bringing food or smoking into the rose garden is prohibited
Guide7: Please throw your trash in the trash can
